{"tid":2137092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[核子手段]核共同社引述解放軍退役軍官指中國擁有高端導彈防禦技術","createTime":"2020-08-02T15:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T16:13:01.000Z","uid":57677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b440f4004c8eff37adfd0cafe815fb2f86e4d5","tid":2137092,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2350241&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=a02e43e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350241</a><br />\n日本共同社引述解放軍退役軍官楊承軍指，中國已具備在落地前探測到敵方發射的核導彈，並用核武器反擊的預警系統。報道指，曾在解放軍核導彈部隊火箭軍服役多年的楊承軍，5月中旬在內地官方雜誌《祖國》電子版上，發表題為《不宜在網絡上炒作涉核問題》的評論，指中國軍方擁有在敵方使用核導彈攻擊的情況下，可在發射後數分鐘內探測、並在落地前進行核反擊的預警系統，強調中國的綜合核戰鬥力不遜色於美俄。 共同社指，如果證實中國擁有高端導彈防禦技術，將改變世界戰略平衡，美國及依靠美國「核保護傘」的日本，不得不調整防衛政策。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2350241&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=a02e43e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350241</a>"},{"pid":"b70d85c89103784aa95b44a86df9f9cc8da87c96","tid":2137092,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"契弟北韓呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3453bc1fe646f391edeeaaba2787d84bdb9f3c","tid":2137092,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea8bc736388330e7ac6fc0e413b979c9f1e8bf1","tid":2137092,"uid":36162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4b440f4004c8eff37adfd0cafe815fb2f86e4d5","tid":2137092,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"原文網址：<a h